# Supabase Configuration (Flutter client only)
# Copy this to .env and fill in your values.
# NEVER commit .env to version control.
#
# SECURITY:
# - Put ONLY client-safe values here (SUPABASE_URL, SUPABASE_ANON_KEY, optional SENTRY_DSN).
# - NEVER put PAYMOB_API_KEY, PAYMOB_HMAC_SECRET, service-role keys, or HMAC secrets in this file.
# - Paymob and other server secrets belong in Supabase Edge Function secrets / a secret manager.
# - If this file is listed under Flutter assets, anything you put here can ship inside the app binary.

SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here
# SENTRY_DSN=
